latestPosts.caption:
Our Bride @makeoverbyaaish Aishaa is wearing a custom-made garara designed exclusively for her — a heartfelt blend of all her chosen colors. This one-of-a-kind piece was brought to life specially for her big day. The garara, like all our signature pieces, is adorned with intricate, high-quality zardozi handwork, generously detailed to celebrate this beautiful moment with grandeur.

Our journey with Aishaa has been incredibly special — from styling her engagement outfit to now being a part of her big day as she steps into a new chapter not just as a bride but also as a makeup artist herself. It’s always beautiful when stories come full circle, and this one truly did.

Makeup: @makeupbybushraimtiyaz
